01:32:44,263 --> 01:32:45,457
What's wrong?

817
01:32:50,135 --> 01:32:51,830
He's dead...

818
01:32:57,142 --> 01:32:59,576
Kawano is dead

819
01:33:04,016 --> 01:33:07,281
<i>Kawano had leukemia, like me</i>

820
01:33:10,923 --> 01:33:14,484
<i>Am I going to die suddenly,
like him?</i>

821
01:33:20,699 --> 01:33:22,633
<i>I'm scared of dying</i>

822
01:33:25,104 --> 01:33:28,073
<i>Parting here
means parting forever</i>

823
01:33:32,077 --> 01:33:35,376
<i>I know you're going to
forget all about me</i>

824
01:33:56,602 --> 01:34:01,733
<i>Sterile Area</i>

825
01:34:50,656 --> 01:34:51,918
Mother

826
01:34:52,891 --> 01:34:55,086
You should go home,
get some sleep

827
01:34:55,628 --> 01:34:58,597
Otherwise, you'll get sick, too

828
01:34:58,697 --> 01:34:59,891
I know that

829
01:34:59,999 --> 01:35:02,229
No, you don't

830
01:35:03,569 --> 01:35:06,697
Oh, I'm fine
I'm going to sleep

831
01:35:06,805 --> 01:35:08,830
Good night

832
01:37:33,685 --> 01:37:35,619
Look at me now

833
01:37:52,004 --> 01:37:54,063
But don't you worry

834
01:37:55,908 --> 01:37:57,705
I'm fine

835
01:38:22,835 --> 01:38:24,359
What is it?

836
01:38:36,615 --> 01:38:41,609
<i>Marriage License Application</i>

837
01:39:19,925 --> 01:39:20,857
Let's get married

838
01:40:28,393 --> 01:40:30,156
I can't...

839
