<i>I know it's last minute,</i>

847
01:41:22,447 --> 01:41:25,541
<i>but I want to take you
to that place I promised you</i>

848
01:41:27,185 --> 01:41:32,145
<i>I'll pick you up
tomorrow, at midnight</i>

849
01:42:17,836 --> 01:42:20,964
You really came to get me

850
01:42:24,409 --> 01:42:26,309
Of course I did

851
01:42:37,322 --> 01:42:39,950
Listen to the wind

852
01:42:51,703 --> 01:42:53,603
It's getting closer

853
01:42:57,742 --> 01:42:59,505
What is?

854
01:43:00,946 --> 01:43:02,413
The typhoon

855
01:43:08,120 --> 01:43:10,020
The typhoon?

856
01:43:13,758 --> 01:43:16,318
Typhoon #29

857
01:43:23,034 --> 01:43:24,797
<i>The super Typhoon #29,</i>

858
01:43:24,903 --> 01:43:27,497
<i>which already hit Kyushu,</i>

859
01:43:27,606 --> 01:43:29,597
<i>wreaking havoc and
paralyzing traffic,</i>

860
01:43:29,708 --> 01:43:31,573
<i>is moving over the water</i>

861
01:43:31,676 --> 01:43:35,237
<i>south of Shikoku,
at 20 kilometers an hour</i>

862
01:43:35,647 --> 01:43:37,581
<i>The typhoon</i>

863
01:43:37,682 --> 01:43:39,775
<i>is expected to hit Shikoku,
with increased ferocity</i>

864
01:43:39,885 --> 01:43:41,648
<i>The rain will grow heavier
this afternoon,</i>

865
01:43:41,753 --> 01:43:44,745
<i>and we are predicting as
much as 200mm total precipitation,</i>

866
01:43:44,856 --> 01:43:47,120
<i>for some areas</i>

867
01:43:47,692 --> 01:43:49,785
<i>In Kyushu, especially in Oita,</i>

868
01:43:49,895 --> 01:43:53,956
<i>we've had many reports of
flooding and landslides</i>

869
01:43:54,533 --> 01:43:56,467
<i>The islands around Okinawa</i>

870
01:43:56,568 --> 01:43:59,332
<i>are already reportedly clear
of the Typhoon...</i>

871
01:44:30,936 --> 01:44:32,301
Say

872
01:44:39,945 --> 01:44:42,573
Your birthday...

873
01:44:46,685 --> 01:44:49,347
is November 3rd, right?

874
01:44:52,857 --> 01:44:54,222
That's right

875
01:44:58,797 --> 01:45:01,561
My birthday...

876
01:45:04,970 --> 01:45:08,303
is October 28th, so...

877
01:45:15,847 --> 01:45:19,010
You haven't had even one second

878
01:45:21,353 --> 01:45:25,346
since your birth,
when I wasn't here, too

879
01:45:34,065 --> 01:45:36,795
Even after I go...

880
01:45:40,972 --> 01:45:44,271
your world will go on

881
