883
01:46:05,196 --> 01:46:06,663
Shut up

884
01:46:08,667 --> 01:46:12,569
<i>This is an announcement
from All Nippon Airways</i>

885
01:46:12,671 --> 01:46:18,200
<i>Flight #327, scheduled to depart
for Tokyo at 6:55 A.M..,</i>

886
01:46:18,310 --> 01:46:21,939
<i>has been cancelled
due to inclement weather</i>

887
01:46:22,080 --> 01:46:25,379
<i>We will handle flight
re-assignments at Counter 3</i>

888
01:46:32,891 --> 01:46:34,085
What do you mean cancelled?

889
01:46:34,192 --> 01:46:36,387
We have to get to Australia!

890
01:46:36,494 --> 01:46:39,588
We don't expect any flights
to take off today

891
01:46:39,731 --> 01:46:41,528
Don't give me that!

892
01:46:41,633 --> 01:46:43,260
We absolutely have to get there!

893
01:46:43,368 --> 01:46:46,565
It's got to be today!
Please! C'mon!

894
01:46:46,671 --> 01:46:47,569
That's enough

895
01:47:01,753 --> 01:47:02,811
Aki!

896
01:47:07,225 --> 01:47:08,453
Aki

897
01:47:09,427 --> 01:47:10,826
Are you OK?

898
01:47:16,768 --> 01:47:18,861
Shall we go back?

899
01:47:22,340 --> 01:47:24,308
Can't we go?

900
01:47:30,348 --> 01:47:34,409
Sure we can
Next time

901
01:47:38,590 --> 01:47:40,922
There won't...

