Wow

920
01:51:53,578 --> 01:51:55,170
<i>You see,</i>

921
01:51:56,614 --> 01:52:01,642
<i>I don't think we should
see each other anymore</i>

922
01:52:04,822 --> 01:52:09,156
<i>The tiny bit of eternity</i>

923
01:52:09,260 --> 01:52:12,024
<i>I spent with you</i>

924
01:52:12,563 --> 01:52:15,396
<i>is the greatest treasure
of my life</i>

925
01:52:19,971 --> 01:52:23,236
<i>I've been so happy with you</i>

926
01:52:33,618 --> 01:52:35,415
<i>That's OK, right?</i>

927
01:52:38,222 --> 01:52:41,123
<i>As of today, let's say goodbye</i>

928
01:52:43,161 --> 01:52:45,288
<i>You'll grow up,</i>

929
01:52:46,631 --> 01:52:48,690
<i>get married,</i>

930
01:52:49,734 --> 01:52:51,793
<i>do your work,</i>

931
01:52:53,371 --> 01:52:57,330
<i>and live into the future
That's what I'm imagining,</i>

932
01:53:00,578 --> 01:53:02,944
<i>as I fall asleep tonight</i>

933
01:53:48,259 --> 01:53:49,851
Hello

934
01:53:52,430 --> 01:53:53,897
<i>Ritsuko</i>

935
01:53:57,635 --> 01:53:59,830
It was you, Saku

936
