died...

941
01:54:37,041 --> 01:54:39,202
I'm so sorry, Saku

942
01:54:43,080 --> 01:54:44,547
<i>Ritsuko</i>

943
01:54:46,250 --> 01:54:47,979
<i>What's happened?</i>

944
01:54:50,288 --> 01:54:53,485
<i>Where are you, now?</i>

945
01:55:06,337 --> 01:55:08,066
The Photo Studio

946
01:55:55,019 --> 01:55:56,509
Sakutaro

947
01:56:03,494 --> 01:56:04,984
Ritsuko?

948
01:56:05,796 --> 01:56:06,888
She went out

949
01:57:01,419 --> 01:57:03,114
Uncle Shige,

950
01:57:06,157 --> 01:57:09,456
