from Aki's death

953
01:57:31,682 --> 01:57:33,809
I can't get over it

954
01:57:35,453 --> 01:57:37,148
Uncle Shige,

955
01:57:38,923 --> 01:57:42,256
I don't know what I should do

956
01:58:07,018 --> 01:58:09,316
It's a big deal,

957
01:58:11,322 --> 01:58:13,222
when someone dies

958
01:58:16,127 --> 01:58:17,754
Memories,

959
01:58:18,362 --> 01:58:20,057
images,

960
01:58:21,098 --> 01:58:24,556
of the happy times, linger
like a stain

961
01:58:33,477 --> 01:58:35,445
Heaven is just something

962
01:58:35,546 --> 01:58:38,845
invented by survivors

963
01:58:41,619 --> 01:58:43,917
My beloved is there

964
01:58:45,089 --> 01:58:47,455
Someday we'll be reunited

965
01:58:51,262 --> 01:58:53,389
We want to believe that

966
01:58:59,970 --> 01:59:03,906
She asked me to give this to you

967
01:59:20,124 --> 01:59:24,458
I still can't let go of this world

968
01:59:25,463 --> 01:59:28,455
A survivor who keeps
clinging to this world

969
01:59:36,707 --> 01:59:39,505
