1015
02:10:15,679 --> 02:10:19,206
<i>and your face,
crumpled up with laughter</i>

1016
02:10:21,384 --> 02:10:24,046
<i>You puffed it up earnestly,</i>

1017
02:10:24,354 --> 02:10:28,484
<i>then suddenly shifted and
