1018
02:10:32,763 --> 02:10:35,698
<i>Your sleeping face on Yume Island</i>

1019
02:10:38,602 --> 02:10:42,595
<i>I wish it was near enough
to touch, now</i>

1020
02:10:47,210 --> 02:10:49,906
<i>When you gave me a ride
on your bike,</i>

1021
02:10:50,013 --> 02:10:53,073
<i>the warmth of your back,</i>

1022
02:10:53,350 --> 02:10:56,046
<i>meant the world to me</i>

1023
02:11:00,023 --> 02:11:03,322
<i>All the memories of time
