02:11:24,314 --> 02:11:27,613
<i>the precious time I spent with you</i>

1028
02:11:34,090 --> 02:11:37,491
<i>I just have one last request</i>

1029
02:11:39,696 --> 02:11:42,028
<i>Please scatter my ashes</i>

1030
02:11:42,833 --> 02:11:46,325
<i>on the winds of Uluru</i>

1031
02:11:47,637 --> 02:11:49,298
<i>And then,</i>

1032
02:11:49,806 --> 02:11:54,072
<i>go on and live your life</i>

1033
02:11:58,315 --> 02:12:01,011
<i>I'm so glad I met you</i>

